    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience. While the interior is clean and well-preserved, you may notice some minor signs of wear on the upholstery consistent with its age. The exterior remains in great shape, though there are a few small scratches and stone chips from regular use. Overall, this is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 35000.0,
